properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 10 at 2:43AM CST until January 12 at 2:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts up to 45 kt and
waves 10 to 15 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 2 AM CST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Some storm force gusts remain possible
particularly along the western side of the lake on Saturday.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.
